{"tid":1840170,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"世一美輸了！票選最美女偶像不是子瑜...是她","createTime":"2020-01-24T17:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T13:30:59.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc2e0fb42b0900bebad340d3b90dd442e1b81e7","tid":1840170,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"南韓大勢女團TWICE台灣成員周子瑜，是公認的神級美顏，近日更成為世界百大美女排行榜第一名，高顏值受到國際肯定，不過在116名現役偶像票選中，去年拿下最美女愛豆的子瑜，今年小下滑一個名次，輸給少女時代的潤娥，而最帥男愛豆仍由去年冠軍ASTRO車銀優蟬聯。<br />\n<br />\n潤娥是少女時代的顏值擔當，出道12年至今，容貌都沒太大變化，凍齡美顏令人稱羨，她在今年訪問了24組共116名偶像中，被選為最美女偶像，可說是實至名歸，而子瑜則和同為四代女團神顏代表的Red Velvet隊長Irene並列第二，小下滑一個名次。而第三名是(G)I-DLE美延，第四名則是秀智、TWICE、ITZY禮志並列，第五名則是少女時代太妍、IZ*ONE玟周。<br />\n<br />\n至於最帥男偶像，還是由去年冠軍、臉蛋天才ASTRO車銀優蟬聯，第二名是BTS的V，第三名是SEVENTEEN勝寬，第四名是GOT7珍榮、NCT在玹並列，第五名則是Golden Child普閔、TXT SOOBIN。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200124000616-260404?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200124000616-260404%3Fchdtv&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=2c67dcd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200124000616-260404?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"debc4f1d7a6793510f4fa0b60f0a6402f7557e62","tid":1840170,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/ed3d250ead5b7371fe8edc56194c8129/6c040186611a94b3-bd/s640x960/c97c8438a06db8cea0eec66eb5116de9dce8888f.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fed3d250ead5b7371fe8edc56194c8129%2F6c040186611a94b3-bd%2Fs640x960%2Fc97c8438a06db8cea0eec66eb5116de9dce8888f.gifv&h=447e66a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/28b3ca7b15e5d7d313cfbf1c73914cff/854b0436feb3574a-81/s400x600/4371afd30144efa2951a4ec1350746fa5008216d.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.t